to explain myself to you.

582
00:30:51,160 --> 00:30:52,690
We bumped into each other
at the airport.

583
00:30:53,400 --> 00:30:55,240
She was going to attend
an exhibition in Shanghai.

584
00:30:56,160 --> 00:30:57,690
Back then, the police called me

585
00:30:57,690 --> 00:30:58,690
and urged me to head back.

586
00:30:59,120 --> 00:30:59,930
She saw me in a hurry,

587
00:31:00,160 --> 00:31:01,490
saying she'd take the cake to you.

588
00:31:01,490 --> 00:31:03,160
I said yes without
thinking too much of it.

589
00:31:04,100 --> 00:31:05,300
(Email delivered successfully)

590
00:31:06,730 --> 00:31:07,610
So, do you feel like

591
00:31:07,610 --> 00:31:08,810
you've been wronged?

592
00:31:14,580 --> 00:31:17,320
(Xia Guo.)

593
00:31:17,320 --> 00:31:18,320
(I already read it.)

594
00:31:19,200 --> 00:31:20,810
(There are something I wish to discuss.)

595
00:31:21,610 --> 00:31:23,280
