at the bar near your house?)

596
00:31:34,360 --> 00:31:34,730
Guo,

597
00:31:34,730 --> 00:31:36,360
I've already explained it
to you many times.

598
00:31:36,360 --> 00:31:37,690
We just have a working relationship.

599
00:31:37,690 --> 00:31:39,040
It's not as complicated as you think.

600
00:31:39,320 --> 00:31:40,240
Working relationship?

601
00:31:41,320 --> 00:31:42,850
Working relationship? Why were you two

602
00:31:42,850 --> 00:31:44,530
that close at the courier station then?

603
00:31:46,570 --> 00:31:47,890
How did you know about that?

604
00:31:47,890 --> 00:31:48,970
You don't want me to find out?

605
00:31:49,160 --> 00:31:50,140
A guilty conscience.

606
00:31:50,280 --> 00:31:51,490
You didn't even dare to mention

607
00:31:51,490 --> 00:31:52,320
the word to me.

608
00:31:52,490 --> 00:31:54,490
Wen Ya is just my client.

609
00:31:54,490 --> 00:31:55,490
That's all.

610
00:31:55,610 --> 00:31:56,360
I didn't mention her

611
00:31:56,440 --> 00:31:58,200
because it doesn't matter
who my clients are.

612
00:31:58,360 --> 00:32:00,040
There's no need
to introduce them to you.

613
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:01,770
Do you want me to introduce

614
00:32:01,770 --> 00:32:02,810
all of my clients to you?

615
00:32:03,570 --> 00:32:04,320
That day,

616
00:32:04,490 --> 00:32:05,970
I was planning to visit the site,

617
00:32:05,970 --> 00:32:06,930
which was her florist.

618
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:08,160
And I was going to mail to you.

619
00:32:08,160 --> 00:32:09,770
That's why I went
to the courier station.

620
00:32:10,970 --> 00:32:12,140
She knew you were in Shanghai.

621
00:32:12,140 --> 00:32:12,980
She was showing me

622
00:32:12,980 --> 00:32:14,490
photos she took in Shanghai before.

623
00:32:14,650 --> 00:32:16,320
What's so indecent about that?

624
00:32:16,570 --> 00:32:18,120
Why do you not trust me at all?

625
00:32:18,490 --> 00:32:19,850
How can I trust you?

626
00:32:21,610 --> 00:32:23,160
I was expecting you to celebrate

627
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:24,160
my birthday together.

628
00:32:24,160 --> 00:32:25,360
What happened in the end?

629
00:32:25,930 --> 00:32:26,730
And,

630
00:32:26,970 --> 00:32:27,770
speaking of trust,

631
00:32:27,770 --> 00:32:29,320
it's your fault that I can't trust you.

632
00:32:29,530 --> 00:32:30,970
You stay in Leshan for your family.

633
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:32,120
You sacrificed me

634
00:32:32,120 --> 00:32:33,120
and our happiness.

635
00:32:33,120 --> 00:32:34,040
Did you know that?

636
00:32:34,040 --> 00:32:35,200
I don't understand this at all.

637
00:32:35,200 --> 00:32:36,970
Why are you bringing up past issues now?

638
00:32:37,970 --> 00:32:38,970
Wanna bring up the past?

639
00:32:39,530 --> 00:32:40,080
Fine.

640
00:32:40,400 --> 00:32:41,980
Something huge happened in the family.

641
00:32:42,080 --> 00:32:42,970
But even now, you showed

642
00:32:42,970 --> 00:32:44,080
no concern for my mother.

643
00:32:44,240 --> 00:32:45,480
You didn't ask how she was doing

644
00:32:45,480 --> 00:32:46,970
or how we should resolve the issue.

645
00:32:47,690 --> 00:32:48,770
Xia Guo,

646
00:32:50,570 --> 00:32:51,690
has my family become

647
00:32:51,690 --> 00:32:53,160
that insignificant to you now?

648
00:32:53,730 --> 00:32:55,650
I showed no concern for your family?

649
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:57,610
Who found the hospital
in Shanghai for you?

650
00:32:58,730 --> 00:32:59,240
In your eyes,

651
00:32:59,320 --> 00:33:01,000
I'm a heartless person, huh?

652
00:33:06,240 --> 00:33:07,440
You're right.

653
00:33:08,690 --> 00:33:09,890
What happened between us

654
00:33:09,890 --> 00:33:10,730
were all caused by

655
00:33:10,730 --> 00:33:11,770
a long-distance relationship.

656
00:33:11,930 --> 00:33:13,040
But you're slaving away here

657
00:33:13,040 --> 00:33:14,160
seven days a week.

658
00:33:14,280 --> 00:33:15,650
I don't see the significance at all.

659
00:33:15,930 --> 00:33:17,080
What other benefits do you have

660
00:33:17,080 --> 00:33:18,120
besides having the money

661
00:33:18,120 --> 00:33:19,440
to buy an extra pair of shoes?

662
00:33:28,120 --> 00:33:29,850
I have nothing to say to you.

663
00:33:31,160 --> 00:33:32,000
This is what you think

664
00:33:32,000 --> 00:33:33,530
about my work in Shanghai, huh?

665
00:33:34,610 --> 00:33:35,440
Fine.

666
00:33:47,530 --> 00:33:48,400
Guo.

667
00:33:49,320 --> 00:33:50,240
Come back.

668
00:33:50,690 --> 00:33:51,440
Return to Leshan.

669
00:33:51,440 --> 00:33:52,200
Let's find back

670
00:33:52,200 --> 00:33:54,650
the happy moments
we used to have in the past.

671
00:33:55,770 --> 00:33:57,650
I can't stand it anymore.

672
00:33:58,690 --> 00:34:00,490
I really need you by my side.

673
00:34:00,850 --> 00:34:02,120
Do you even need me?

674
00:34:02,850 --> 00:34:04,040
You don't need me at all.

675
00:34:04,040 --> 00:34:05,040
You just need someone

676
00:34:05,040 --> 00:34:06,400
