677
00:34:06,810 --> 00:34:08,000
What do you mean by that?

678
00:34:09,400 --> 00:34:11,490
How could that person not be you?

679
00:34:14,080 --> 00:34:16,240
More like you're the one
who no longer needs me.

680
00:34:19,530 --> 00:34:20,650
Just be direct with me.

681
00:34:20,930 --> 00:34:21,530
What?

682
00:34:21,770 --> 00:34:23,080
You wanna break up with me or what?

683
00:34:23,080 --> 00:34:24,080
Just be direct with me.

684
00:34:24,650 --> 00:34:25,890
Yu Jian, have you lost your mind?

685
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:27,850
Do you know what you're saying?

686
00:34:27,850 --> 00:34:28,810
I don't know!

687
00:34:28,890 --> 00:34:29,440
I only know

688
00:34:29,440 --> 00:34:30,970
that I shouldn't have come today!

689
00:34:30,970 --> 00:34:32,570
Leave, then!

690
00:35:43,040 --> 00:35:44,200
Yu Jian!

691
00:35:46,850 --> 00:35:47,530
Mr. Xue.

692
00:35:47,770 --> 00:35:48,970
You'll regret it if you go.

693
00:35:49,570 --> 00:35:50,690
No, I have to go after him!

694
00:35:50,850 --> 00:35:51,360
No!

695
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:53,400
Don't do this! I'm out of time!

696
00:35:53,970 --> 00:35:55,160
You already saw him just now.

697
00:35:58,200 --> 00:35:58,970
Were you happy?

698
00:35:59,040 --> 00:36:00,320
Ask yourself this. Were you happy?

699
00:36:03,040 --> 00:36:04,930
I couldn't be happy at all.

700
00:36:05,040 --> 00:36:06,650
I couldn't.

701
00:36:07,200 --> 00:36:08,650
Now, I'll tell you the second one.

702
00:36:09,690 --> 00:36:10,770
Initiate the breakup.

703
00:36:13,360 --> 00:36:14,490
The one who initiates

704
00:36:14,610 --> 00:36:15,810
