705
00:36:19,120 --> 00:36:21,080
But I'm in pain right now.

706
00:36:24,280 --> 00:36:26,730
My heart is in pain
when I think about him.

707
00:36:26,970 --> 00:36:27,850
I...

708
00:36:42,360 --> 00:36:44,280
Alright now. Calm down.

709
00:36:50,930 --> 00:36:52,040
Why?

710
00:36:52,650 --> 00:36:53,610
Why?

711
00:36:53,970 --> 00:36:54,770
Why are you...

712
00:36:54,890 --> 00:36:56,060
Why?

713
00:36:56,060 --> 00:36:58,570
You shouldn't be here!

714
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:43,400
Yu Jian, you're awake.

715
00:37:44,530 --> 00:37:45,440
What are you doing here?

716
00:37:47,360 --> 00:37:49,000
Mrs. Yu told me to come.

717
00:37:56,120 --> 00:37:57,240
You never spoke a single word

718
00:37:57,730 --> 00:37:58,810
