719
00:37:59,200 --> 00:38:01,000
Your parents were terrified.

720
00:38:04,320 --> 00:38:06,000
Luckily, your fever has subsided.

721
00:38:08,570 --> 00:38:09,400
Where are my parents?

722
00:38:09,930 --> 00:38:12,040
Mrs. Yu brought Mr. Yu
to the park to play chess.

723
00:38:13,810 --> 00:38:14,490
Don't worry.

724
00:38:14,970 --> 00:38:16,970
Mrs. Yu told the guard
to carry Mr. Yu on his back.

725
00:38:20,320 --> 00:38:21,080
I can't cook well.

726
00:38:21,570 --> 00:38:22,610
Don't be picky, okay?

727
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:26,850
Here.

728
00:38:27,200 --> 00:38:28,400
Try it while it's hot.

729
00:38:34,650 --> 00:38:36,320
Why did you come back in a hurry?

730
00:38:36,570 --> 00:38:38,610
Was your girlfriend still angry at you?

731
00:38:41,890 --> 00:38:42,770
That's not it.

732
00:38:43,810 --> 00:38:44,570
She was just busy.

733
00:38:45,970 --> 00:38:47,200
Don't lie to me.

734
00:38:47,970 --> 00:38:49,650
She has a misunderstanding toward me.

735
00:38:50,000 --> 00:38:52,160
Did she make it hard
by talking about me?

736
00:38:54,810 --> 00:38:55,770
No.

737
00:38:57,690 --> 00:38:58,570
I'm glad to hear that.

738
00:38:59,690 --> 00:39:00,770
Actually, I came here

739
00:39:01,200 --> 00:39:02,810
to give you something.

740
00:39:04,400 --> 00:39:06,730
I think you need it right now.

741
00:39:15,730 --> 00:39:17,080
Alright now. I won't bother you.

742
00:39:17,080 --> 00:39:18,810
You should sleep longer. See you later.

743
00:39:55,890 --> 00:39:57,570
Wen Ya, wait.

744
00:40:02,400 --> 00:40:03,490
I can't accept your money.

745
00:40:05,160 --> 00:40:06,320
You deserve this.

746
00:40:06,690 --> 00:40:08,220
An advance payment for your design.

747
00:40:08,280 --> 00:40:09,580
But this is too much.

748
00:40:09,810 --> 00:40:11,120
This is just half of it.

749
00:40:11,240 --> 00:40:12,160
I'll transfer the rest

750
00:40:12,280 --> 00:40:14,320
one month after
the initiation of the project.

751
00:40:15,850 --> 00:40:16,850
Yu Jian,

752
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:17,810
you aren't just

753
00:40:17,810 --> 00:40:19,280
any ordinary designer in my heart.

754
00:40:19,810 --> 00:40:20,400
Your worth

755
00:40:20,490 --> 00:40:21,970
cannot be measured with money.

756
00:40:23,570 --> 00:40:25,040
If you lose money, you can earn it back.

757
00:40:25,610 --> 00:40:26,610
If you lose your love,

758
00:40:27,320 --> 00:40:28,240
you can find another one.

759
00:40:30,040 --> 00:40:31,690
Everything will definitely get better.

760
00:40:32,930 --> 00:40:35,040
But you mustn't give up on yourself.

761
00:40:40,320 --> 00:40:41,690
You're doing me a huge favor here.

762
00:40:42,610 --> 00:40:43,610
I'm truly thankful to you.

763
00:40:43,690 --> 00:40:44,200
Don't worry.

764
00:40:44,530 --> 00:40:46,000
I'll definitely do a good job.

765
00:40:47,240 --> 00:40:48,360
Thank you so much.

766
00:40:50,360 --> 00:40:51,280
I'm not just being nice

767
00:40:52,040 --> 00:40:53,320
to you because of the project.

768
00:40:55,320 --> 00:40:56,610
Actually,

769
00:40:57,650 --> 00:40:59,240
I do like you quite a lot.

770
00:41:01,890 --> 00:41:04,040
I don't believe
that you didn't feel it at all.

771
00:41:04,650 --> 00:41:06,690
You blocked off everything

772
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:09,770
as you were together with
Xia Guo before this.

773
00:41:10,730 --> 00:41:12,040
But now, it's different.

774
00:41:12,570 --> 00:41:14,160
I hope you can reconsider your decision.

775
00:41:14,890 --> 00:41:15,970
I hope you can consider me.

776
00:41:16,570 --> 00:41:17,970
Wen Ya, actually, I...

777
00:41:17,970 --> 00:41:19,000
Yu Jian,

778
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:20,770
I know. You can't get over her.

779
00:41:21,360 --> 00:41:22,400
But it's fine.

780
00:41:23,690 --> 00:41:24,570
From tomorrow onward,

781
00:41:24,570 --> 00:41:26,040
I can keep you company every day.

782
00:41:26,930 --> 00:41:28,040
I believe

783
00:41:28,610 --> 00:41:30,610
that you'll accept me one day.

784
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:37,240
Thank you

785
00:41:37,890 --> 00:41:39,360
for giving me this opportunity.

786
00:41:41,000 --> 00:41:43,000
We can work hard together.

787
00:42:15,080 --> 00:42:16,000
Yu Jian,

788
00:42:16,000 --> 00:42:16,810
I'll head back first.

789
00:42:17,080 --> 00:42:18,240
You guys can have a chat.

790
00:42:20,930 --> 00:42:21,650
See you tomorrow.

791
00:42:22,040 --> 00:42:23,200
You must remember what I said.

792
00:42:23,970 --> 00:42:25,160
I trust you.

793
00:42:55,850 --> 00:42:56,970
What else do you want to say?

794
00:42:57,360 --> 00:42:58,360
You already saw it.

795
00:42:59,160 --> 00:43:00,280
What's with the question?

796
00:43:01,810 --> 00:43:03,890
Is this your so-called
"working relationship"?

797
00:43:04,570 --> 00:43:06,080
Is this "there's nothing indecent

798
00:43:06,080 --> 00:43:07,040
