806
00:43:32,360 --> 00:43:33,240
Fine.

807
00:43:34,530 --> 00:43:36,080
You're even saying
the same thing as her.

808
00:43:36,850 --> 00:43:38,200
Is she very gentle,

809
00:43:38,890 --> 00:43:40,650
