820
00:44:01,000 --> 00:44:02,490
You can think whatever you like.

821
00:44:04,040 --> 00:44:04,850
That's right.

822
00:44:06,120 --> 00:44:07,200
Not only did she help me out,

823
00:44:07,810 --> 00:44:09,080
