826
00:44:11,890 --> 00:44:13,320
Why is she the one helping me out

827
00:44:13,320 --> 00:44:14,440
instead of you?

828
00:44:15,360 --> 00:44:16,400
What about you?

829
00:44:17,320 --> 00:44:18,530
What were you doing?

830
00:44:24,320 --> 00:44:25,730
Let's drop the act now.

831
00:44:26,970 --> 00:44:28,200
Let's part ways in peace.

